of general staff of the Zairian Armed Forces, there have been 
rebel infiltrations from a neighboring country into the 
Ruwenzori and Wataninga areas in North Kivu. After combat 
troops were dispatched to the affected areas, the Zairian Armed 
Forces rapidly repelled the invaders, kicking them out of our 
country. [passage omitted] 

