yesterday threatened to call a nationwide strike of schools and 
colleges if Secretary-General Abdulraham Wandati of the Islamic 
Party of Kenya and the chairman of the Universities Academic 
Staff Union, Dr Korwa Adar, are not released unconditionally. 
Sheikh Balala told the government that by arresting innocent 
