<H3> <TI>   Bophuthatswana Urges International Mediation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0203082294 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 0500 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0203082294 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Bophuthatswana's chief negotiator, Mr. Rowan Cronje, 
says Bophuthatswana will consider registering for the election 
if international mediators are called in to resolve issues. Mr. 
Cronje told our political news staff that the Freedom Alliance 
had always said that it would be prepared to look at 
