<H3> <TI>   Former Italian Embassy Comes Under Fire </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0403113094 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1045 
GMT 4 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0403113094 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Due Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Italian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] We have just heard that for about half an hour this 
morning about 20 Somalis directed fire at the former Italian 
Embassy in Mogadishu, in which a unit of the Italian contingent 
is based. 
  Guards returned fire, as did the crews on two caterpillar 
vehicles that were returning to the base when they also came 
under attack. 
  No Italians have been hurt. The Somalis fled shortly 
afterward and it is not known if any of them were hurt. The 
motives behind the attack are not yet known. 

</TEXT>

