<F P=102>  MB0403055794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1730 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0403055794 </F>
<F P=104>  Maputo Radio Mozambique Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] As was the case yesterday, another meeting of the 
Cease- Fire Commission failed to take place in Maputo this 
afternoon, because of the absence of the Mozambique National 
Resistance's delegation. The meeting was scheduled to discuss 
four main points: the destruction of obsolete war materiel at 
assembly areas, the transfer of weapons from assembly areas to 
regional depots, the start of demobilization process, and 
incidents in some assembly areas belonging to Renamo. 

</TEXT>

