<F P=102>  MB0203185594 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1730 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0203185594 </F>
<F P=104>  Maputo Radio Mozambique Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In Maputo this afternoon President of the Republic 
Joaquim Chissano received Kenyan Foreign Minister Stephen 
Musyoka. Radio Mozambique learned that the meeting was aimed at 
boosting cooperation between the two countries, for development 
and exchange of experiences in the fields of cooperation, 
health, trade, education, and culture. Stephen Musyoka returns 
to his country tomorrow. 
