<H3> <TI>   Abacha Discusses Cameroon Situation With Eyadema </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB0303190594 Paris AFP in French 1836 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> AB0303190594 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Abuja, 3 Mar (AFP) -- A source close to the Nigerian 
presidency stated that Nigerian President Sani Abacha discussed 
the border dispute between his country and Cameroon with 
Togolese counterpart Gnassingbe Eyadema today. The source did 
not specify the content of the discussion, but indicated that 
the meeting -- which took place in the presidential lounge of 
