<H3> <TI>   New Political Party Founded, Supports Federalism </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0403185794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1730 GMT 4 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0403185794 </F>
<F P=104>  Maputo Radio Mozambique Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Another political party has been founded in 
Mozambique. It is called the Mozambique Internationalist 
Democratic Party, Pidemo, founded by Joao Kamacho. The party 
views federalism as the best system of government to guarantee 
the country's development. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

