<F P=103> MB0403154894 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SAPA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Andrew Thimson] </F>
  [Text] Johannesburg March 4 SAPA -- The Green Party led by 
Nathan Grant on Friday afternoon became the 22nd party to 
register for the April elections. The party is registered in the 
Western Cape only, said a spokesman for the Independent 
Electoral Commission [IEC]. The IEC gave the party's telephone 
number as (021) 531- 1774. 

